rComments: DO NOT TAKE THIS CLASS. She is extremely rude and her final was the worst thing ever. I absolutely hated this class. Stay away from her and the class.

Regina is a very laid-back professor who doesn't put too much pressure on students and makes the work load pretty bearable. The films she shows are kind of slow but there were a couple good ones in the mix. She will call you out if you aren't listening/aren't doing your assignments but she means well.
WORST TEACHER EVER.  She is so rude and doesn't care about her students at all.  She shouldn't even be teaching.  AVOID THIS CLASS!!!!!!

DO NOT TAKE A CLASS WITH PROFESSOR LONGO YOU WILL REGRET IT. She doesn't care about her students and their success. The homework and midterm were simple and straightforward enough, but the final was absurd! She didn't prepare the class for the final whatsoever. She will not help you if you ask and is extremely condescending.

Horrible!! Doesn't answer questions but tells you you'll need to know what you don't know for the exam. Doesn't seem to respect students. Powerpoints are made up of artwork and paragraph long quotes. Not engaging and will call you out for leaving early-bit ridiculous for such a big class. Please avoid taking any class with her. You will regret it.

DO NOT TAKE THIS CLASS!!!I went to her office hours and she was behaving so mean.The homework and midterm are easy, but the final is super dumb and ridiculous! Taking this class as a GE was a mistake!

DO NOT TAKE THIS CLASS. She is so rude and is extremely annoying. She gave us extremely easy homework and midterm that wasn't hard without doing any of the reading. She expects you to memorize the reading in the final. DONT EVEN TAKE FOR A GE YOU WILL REGRET IT. AVOID THIS CLASS!!!!!!!

Homework and Midterm is a breeze. A LOT OF READING. A lot of the things are subjective, no definite right or wrong answers. Poor teaching style. Powerpoints that put you to sleep. The final is simply ridiculous. DO NOT TAKE.

She will laugh at you if you respond with an answer that she finds dumb. She likes to stare at the class in silence for 15 seconds and continuously sniffs. The homework and midterm are pretty easy, but she bombards you with things on the final. Boring lectures! Don't take any class from her!
